snippet.title: Believe All Victims Unless They're Imperfect: Zayn Malik, Yolanda Hadid, & The Amber Heard Effect
snippet.description:
In this video, I discuss the situation with Zayn Malik and his partner, Gigi Hadid's mother, Yolanda Hadid. I want to drive home that this is deeper than the issue at hand. Just because an alleged victim is unlikable does not mean they're not a victim. Just because an alleged perpetrator is likable does not mean they're innocent. There are no perfect victims.

Bitch Media article:
https://www.bitchmedia.org/article/johnny-depp-amber-heard-cycles-of-abuse
